Little Cigars: $1.36 per 20 cigars;
Snuff: $1.19/oz. and a proportionate rate on fractional parts of an ounce;
All other tobacco products: 50% of the wholesale sales price.
IOWA CODE § 453A.43 (2007).

Retailer cigarette permit: $50 to $100 annually, depending on local population size;
Wholesaler, distributor, or cigarette vendor permit: $100 annually;
Tobacco products distributor license: $100 annually unless the person already has a permit of any kind to deal in cigarettes.
